      <description>Biography I am a software engineer at in the semiconductor division at Samsung Electronics. At KAIST, I researched modeling and simulation of complex semiconductor tools, and developed a new prediction model that is accurate and robust, with little extra computational complexity. At Samsung, I initially worked as a cloud/systems engineer on our big data analytics cloud platform. I now work as a software engineer and develop libraries for analyzing semiconductor data.</description>
